  #home-section-2.home-section
    .row
      .col-md-8.offset-md-2.col-10.offset-1
        %p{ style: 'text-align:center'} Nomad Credit is a financial marketplace for those underserved by other marketplaces. We aim to find the right financial product for international students and/or visa holders currently or planning to live in the U.S. The main visa holders we serve are F1, J1, L1 and H-1B visas. Nomad Credit allows international students and visa holders to search for education loans, education loan refinancing, personal loans, auto loans, auto insurance, student medical insurance, renters insurance and credit cards. Based upon the information provided in a search, Nomad Credit will provide the potential financial options for that international student or visa holder.  


        %br
        %p{ style: 'text-align:center'} We allow international students and visa holders to become aware of and evaluate the different financial options that they may have available by connecting them to the lenders and financial institutions that may be able to serve them. Not all lenders and institutions will serve international students and/or visa holders currently or planning to live in the U.S. Nomad Credit has identified and brought together the lenders and institutions that do. We believe in reducing the barriers to credit for those not currently adequately served in the U.S. financial system.
  
  #home-section-4.home-section{ style: 'padding-bottom:50px'}
