        %h3 WHAT IS THE NOMAD CREDIT FINANCIAL MARKETPLACE? 
        %p{ style: 'text-align:center;font-size:1.3rem'}
          Nomad Credit’s financial marketplace is a central location where international students and visa holders can search for numerous financial products; including education loans (also known as student loans), education loan refinancing, personal loans, auto loans, auto insurance, student medical insurance, renters insurance, credit cards and international payments. We allow international students and visa holders to become aware of and evaluate the different financial options that they may have available by connecting them to the lenders and financial institutions that may be able to serve them. 

 

